    cta: 'Join Our Bible Study in Sandton',
    areaNotes: [
      'Sandton is our main contact point for visitors who want clear directions, Korean class registration, and youth program information.',
      'If you live or work around Sandton, Parkmore, Morningside, Bryanston, or nearby suburbs, this is the easiest place to start.',
