    cta: 'Join Our Bible Study in Alberton',
    areaNotes: [
      'Alberton helps us serve people south of Johannesburg who are searching for Bible study and a sincere Christian community.',
      'Please call for current details, especially if you are joining for the first time or bringing family members.',
